Title: "Mommy\u2019s dream"
DateModified: '2019-03-10'
DatePublished: '2019-03-10'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/mommy-s-dream
SetInCountry: Brazil
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: "D\xE9bora  Almeida"
AuthorCountry: Brazil
Text: Was the 50th birthday of a mother, her dream was to meet somewhere in europe.
  Her daughter won a wonderful trip to Portugal, the land of their ancestors! Arriving
  there, they were so amazed by the food and the places, that they were easily impressed
  with each experience. They won the trip, but also the chance to reconnect and get
  to know each other better, in a country of beautiful beaches and historical monuments.
